title: Accessibility
description: The Metropolitan Washington Airports Authority is fully committed to providing universal access to all public facilities and services at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport for all of its patrons. Washington, DC, is considered one of the most accessible cities in the United States. The Metropolitan Washington Airports Authority is working to ensure that this very important gateway to our Nation's Capital is also accessible to all patrons. For more information visit: http://www.metwashairports.com/reagan/231.htm

title: Parking
description:
Terminal Parking
Park in any garage and pay hourly for up to four hours, or park longer and pay the maximum daily rate. Select the parking (A, B or C) with the same letter as your terminal for the closest access via moving walkways. Free airport shuttle service is also available between the garages and all terminals.

title: Rail
description: The Washington, DC Metrorail system has an elevated Metrorail station connected to the concourse level of terminals B and C at Reagan National Airport. Metrorail farecards may be purchased at machines located at all entrances to the Airport Metrorail station. The station is also fully accessible via elevators.

title: Rental Cars
description: On-Airport rental car counters are located on the first floor in Parking Garage A. Club members of each rental car company may proceed directly to the 2nd or 3rd floor of Garage A.

title: Taxis and Public Transportation
description: Taxicabs are dispatched from convenient locations on the arrivals curb just outside the baggage claim areas of each terminal. Uniformed taxicab dispatchers are stationed at each taxicab dispatch area to assist passengers with selecting a taxicab based on destinations in Washington DC, Virginia, or Maryland.

description: Free Wi-Fi access is available throughout the airport.

title: Parking
description:
Economy Parking
Intended for long stays, is located away from the terminal and is served by free airport shuttles to all terminals. $15/day.
